Giant Enemy Crabs
[[Image:GIANT CRAB.jpg|thumb|Historically Accurate]]
{{notcrap}}
In the past, one of the biggest threats to the Japanese way of life was that of '''Giant Enemy Crabs'''. The only way the samurai of old could defeat these terrors was by flipping them over with real time weapon change, then attacking their weak point for [[massive damage]].

